
tinyfont specification

+------------------+---------------------------------------------+
| Bytes            | Description                                 |
+------------------+---------------------------------------------+
| 8                | "tinyfont" magic number                     |
+------------------+---------------------------------------------+
| 2                | em size = ascent + descent                  |
+------------------+---------------------------------------------+
| 2,[2,2]          | maplen, [rune, offset]                      |
+------------------+---------------------------------------------+
| 2,2,2,[12|12|28] | rune, glyphwidth, cmdlen, [xym|xyl|xyxyxyc] |
+------------------+---------------------------------------------+
All values are in big endian;
Offset is from end of map.
Point coordinates are in IEEE 754 "Binary32".
